column16: Alex Rios grounds into double play, shortstop Cody Ransom to second baseman Robinson Cano to first baseman Jason Giambi.    Marco Scutaro out at 2nd.
Marco Scutaro singles on a line drive to right fielder Xavier Nady.    Gregg Zaun scores.    Joe Inglett to 3rd.
Joe Inglett walks.    Gregg Zaun to 2nd.
Travis Snider flies out to left fielder Melky Cabrera.
Jim Thome grounds out, shortstop Cody Ransom to first baseman Juan Miranda.
Jerry Owens grounds out, first baseman Juan Miranda to pitcher Humberto Sanchez.
Paul Phillips called out on strikes.
